 question, whether the strong first-order phase transition needed\nfor baryogenesis can be realized in IDM. A region with a good DM relic density\nand a strong first-order phase transition is established, and discussed in the\nlight of the XENON-100 data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Apr 2013 19:45:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 30 Apr 2013 15:21:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-05-01"}
